      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i've heard people say it's fine since it's just fruit and it's full of vitamins. i usually take it with a lot of juice anyway so it's not like a huge amount. are you sure it's actually dangerous? i don't really have time to make an appointment with my doctor just for a glass of juice lol",
